{"tid":1978819,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭條孖寶無懼被「圍剿」繼續諷刺時弊：如無可笑之處，如何被人嘲笑？","createTime":"2020-04-19T04:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T08:42:06.000Z","uid":125168,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c08b67cc23a999816c760ec2891f0c868ef1f1","tid":1978819,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"【打壓港台】頭條孖寶無懼被「圍剿」繼續諷刺時弊：如無可笑之處，如何被人嘲笑？<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200419/R3UMU7WB2X4EMGKFV67MI5JQGU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200419%2FR3UMU7WB2X4EMGKFV67MI5JQGU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDsljX8qB7Opg6os1DAz3scM%3D&h=6323742d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200419%2FR3UMU7WB2X4EMGKFV67MI5JQGU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=d7f5ce5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200419/R3UMU7WB2X4EMGKFV67MI5JQGU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n挖苦諷刺比嚴肅評論來得更一針見血，正因如此，更容易開罪別人。長年受到親政府團體狙擊的香港電台，近日被捲進政治漩渦。揶揄時弊的《頭條新聞》首當其衝，嘲諷警方抗疫，換來一哥史無前例投訴至通訊局。擔任節目主持十多年的吳志森與曾志豪接受《蘋果》專訪時指，節目啟播31年，今年終迎來最猛烈攻擊，警方、顧委會及商經局「裏應外合」，「誓捉到你人頭落地為止」，但二人強調無意收斂，只會更加尖銳針砭時弊，「如你無可笑之處，又如何被人嘲笑？」<br />\n<br />\n記者 李詠希<br />\n<br />\n吳續說，《頭條新聞》是言論自由的指標，「當然會拮到人，會痛甚至流血，但正常嘅社會或開放自由嘅社會，正正需要呢種拮到當權者痛嘅媒體作品存在。如唔容許呢啲作品存在，社會係畸形嘅。就算換咗主持，《頭條新聞》嘅風格同作用，係唔可以改變，而且要越做越尖銳。」<br />\n<br />\n曾志豪指，諷刺需要留白，讓人自行意會，當一個諷刺時弊的節目多人喜愛，代表民智越高，同時反映社會怨氣越重。他笑指《頭條新聞》就像按摩技師，按中市民對當權者的不滿，「如你無可笑之處，又如何被人嘲笑？」他又「多謝政府」提供靈感，「佢哋搞到一鑊粥，我哋咪有飯開囉。所謂有飯開，即係好多新聞源源不絕咁由佢哋而嚟。我哋都希望有日可以粗茶淡飯，佢做好就國泰民安喇」。"},{"pid":"d578790912c9987d2468741acbfddf76a84da6f8","tid":1978819,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"支持港台<br />\n<br />\n幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ccc1c0323f4cbd13d5f2cd4c6b13b9c482c7a8f","tid":1978819,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17906438e8a6b32890c57d07eb5474137a1e0da0","tid":1978819,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"每個星期五都準時睇 驚訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d54a645884ebae3842c08aa08b02a560c64548","tid":1978819,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d578790912c9987d2468741acbfddf76a84da6f8","tid":1978819,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"支持港台<br />\n<br />\n幫推「資訊戰」 有個痴線佬準備好晒中宣部旗下Youtuber嘅report<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b0dcb2ec99c03e17d4d5eb8d6bcd484fa2ed81","tid":1978819,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f7678f6d77f2ba3c8bc